say hello 5 times.

System.out.println("Hello");
System.out.println("Hello");
System.out.println("Hello");
System.out.println("Hello");
System.out.println("Hello");

while loop - repets block of code based on the condition

int time=10;

if(time<12){
	System.out.println("Morning"); //1
}
------------------------------------------------

while(time<12){
	System.out.println("Morning"); //infinite
}